## Limitations
This report is limited by the availability of data and the potential biases in the sources reviewed. The analysis primarily relies on secondary sources, which may reflect the authors' perspectives. Additionally, the long-term effects of the tax cuts are still unfolding, and future analyses may provide more definitive conclusions.